javamoon.construct.binary
Class ClassConstructor

java.lang.Object
  javamoon.construct.binary.ClassConstructor

public class ClassConstructor
extends java.lang.Object

Constructor of a class features from a binary class. This happens when source code is not available, since we use the .class file. It manages the field, constructor and methods of a class.

Since:
JavaMoon-2.0
Author:
Raúl Marticorena
